    <item>
      <title>摩根士丹利因电动汽车需求疲软而下调价格目标后特斯拉股价下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/tesla-shares-fall-after-morgan-stanley-cuts-price-target-weakening-ev-demand-2024-03-06/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周三，特斯拉股价连续第三天下跌，此前摩根士丹利一位备受关注的分析师下调了该股的目标价，称尽管大幅降价，但包括中国在内的主要市场的电动汽车需求仍在继续疲软。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/tesla-shares-fall-after-morgan-stanley-cuts-price-target-weakening-ev-demand-2024-03-06/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 17:43:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
